{"word":"ἀνδρίζω","slug":"ἀνδρίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνδρίζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀνήρ'><el>ἀνήρ</el></a>\n<p/><i>to make a man of</i>: <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> or <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to come to manhood, behave like a man, play the man</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/>"}]}